{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"176817-ghan-biladi-shanku-biladi","title":"घन बिलाड़ि! शंकु बिलाड़ि!","description":"एहि पोथीक बिलाड़ि कें रंग - बिरंगक आकृतिसभ बड़ पसिन छै | बिलाड़ि आ ओकर नान्हि संगीक संग अहूँलोकन्हि रंग-बिरंगक आकृतिसभ पर कनेक नजर दियौ।  \r\n","language":"Maithili","langCode":"mai","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["REKHA THAKUR"],"illustrators":["Rajiv Eipe"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/176817-ghan-biladi-shanku-biladi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720849/size3/129b533b0a0d7b69a71cff6ce379b5a3.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720849/size6/129b533b0a0d7b69a71cff6ce379b5a3.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34006/size6/d0c8274fac1006c3dd5aee668658c805.jpg","text":"त्रिकोण बा तिकोन आकारक \nछत पर देह ऐंठैत बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34007/size6/d1eae14b526ad7c58d62b395d59fab11.jpg","text":"आयत आकारक चौकोन जङला बा\nखिड़कीसँ तकैत बिलाड़ि।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34010/size6/b1ef98473dd14195af4831c362ed68df.jpg","text":"कँपैत बिलाड़ि पर घनाकार बरफक खण्ड\nम्याऊँ.. किट्.. किट्.. किट्..\nओह, कतेक ठण्ढा!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34011/size6/dc2aee5907b0a1744cdf67cdab5f8a6b.jpg","text":"चतुर्भुज आकारक गुड्डी उड़बैत बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34012/size6/d1480cd0d2007b2aeaaa7b00370350e1.jpg","text":"वर्गाकार पट्ट\nपर चौसारि \nखेलैत बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34013/size6/f8e1abe728c304f3e1355146a05d39fd.jpg","text":"म्याऊँ.. खर्र.. खर्र..\nपंजासँ नोछरैत बिलाड़ि\n।\nबेलन आकारक गाछक डारि देखि प्रसन्न बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34014/size6/f2fe57b03f03197946740671fa5f8d28.jpg","text":"गोल बा वृत आकारक \nआसनी पर\nऔंघाएत बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34015/size6/fa3786c705c687d39451bf094133d234.jpg","text":"अण्डा आकारक अएनामे \nमुँह निहारैत बिलाड़ि।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34016/size6/ed577f203b1f1fc88bd5a73c7ffb7aa9.jpg","text":"म्याऊँ.. सुरुक.. सुरुक\nशंकु आकारक आइसक्रीम कोण पाबि गदगद बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34017/size6/cf4df52a26f39b9d291fd472b09326cc.jpg","text":"षटकोण आकारक \nमधुमाछीक\nछत्ता लग ठाढ़ बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34018/size6/d0b5627dd9d460b9b31ba0182fb2790b.jpg","text":"अर्धचंद्राकार बा\nआधा चानक \nबारेमे कल्पना\nकरैत बिलाड़ि\n।","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34020/size6/3778a37378f99b8f767bd316eeff6f48.jpg","text":"भूखसँ तपाएल\nबिलाड़ि लेल\nपिरामिड आकारक समोसा\n।\nम्याउँ ....\nकुर्र...\nकुर्र!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34021/size6/6594a387af7313904fdecf3af97ac6f9.jpg","text":"1.  त्रिकोण\n2.  वर्ग\n3.  आयत\n4.  अण्डाकार \n5.  वृत","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34022/size6/2b23c99e1c444e4eb3e9e23788af8911.jpg","text":"1.  घन\n2.  बेलन / थम्ब \n3.  कोण / शंकु \n4.  पिरामिड \n5. गोलाकार","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34023/size6/0bcaceaf4b8d03101c711191b7cbc92a.jpg","text":"की अहाँ अपन चारू कात आन-आन तरहक आकारसभ आ ओहिसँ\nखेलाएत बिलाड़ि ताकि सकैत छी?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":153}}